### LIST - sin parámetros (page=1, per_page=10, order_by=company_name asc)
GET http://localhost:8001/customers
Accept: application/json

### LIST - paginación (página 2, 5 registros por página)
GET http://localhost:8001/customers?page=2&per_page=5
Accept: application/json

### LIST - filtro por nombre (contiene "rest")
GET http://localhost:8001/customers?name_filter=rest
Accept: application/json

### LIST - ordenación descendente por país
GET http://localhost:8001/customers?order_by=country&order_direction=desc
Accept: application/json

### LIST - combinación de todo
GET http://localhost:8001/customers?page=1&per_page=5&name_filter=a&order_by=company_name&order_direction=desc
Accept: application/json

### Cliente existente (ALFKI es un id clasico de Northwind)
GET http://localhost:8001/customers/ALFKI
Accept: application/json

### Cliente inexistente -> 404
GET http://localhost:8001/customers/ZZZZZ
Accept: application/json

### CREATE - Crear un cliente nuevo
POST http://localhost:8001/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_id": "TEST1",
  "company_name": "Empresa de Prueba",
  "contact_name": "Carlos Bach",
  "contact_title": "Owner",
  "address": "Calle Falsa 123",
  "city": "Madrid",
  "region": null,
  "postal_code": "28001",
  "country": "Spain",
  "phone": "+34 600 000 000",
  "fax": null
}

### UPDATE - Actualizar el cliente creado
PUT http://localhost:8001/customers/TEST1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_id": "TEST1",
  "company_name": "Empresa de Prueba S.L.",
  "contact_name": "Carlos B.",
  "contact_title": "CEO",
  "address": "Gran Via 1",
  "city": "Madrid",
  "region": null,
  "postal_code": "28013",
  "country": "Spain",
  "phone": "+34 600 111 222",
  "fax": null
}

### DELETE - Borrar el cliente creado
DELETE http://localhost:8001/customers/TEST1
Accept: application/json
